main event: An unidentified object was spotted in the sky near the head of a key in Bountiful, Utah, on July 13, 1956.
interesting points: The observer had a 15-minute long sighting,The object was described as a triangular silhouette with a metallic gray color,The observer, a 60-year-old man, was not particularly excited and doubted it was an unusual aircraft,The observer potentially mistook the sighting for a weather phenomenon or mirage,The weather was clear during the observation.
